text_entities.TRANSLATED_TEXT: Guys, in connection with the upcoming holidays (Christmas and New Year), I would like to remind and ask all of you to join in supporting our guys at the front who are fighting for us and your/our safety every day. I am sure that we are all now thinking about gifts, how to celebrate the holidays in comfort, but believe me, without our help, the guys will have neither holidays nor gifts. They stand so that we can live. Let's help them survive. Please, everyone who wants to support our guys from the Armed Forces of Ukraine - let's pitch in a little. At the moment, I, as a volunteer and moderator of this chat for over two years who helps everyone - ask everyone who can help, to support our guys and send a donation to my PayPal:

Those who have known me for more than a day perfectly understand that we will honestly allocate the collected amount to where it is really and urgently needed. We help as much as we can and as long as we are in the rear and not on the front line, it is our duty. I guarantee a report on where the donations will go üòâ
